longBusinessSummary: Terranet AB engages in the development of technical solutions for Advanced Driver Assistance Systems (ADAS) in vehicles. The company is involved in the development of BlincVision, anti-collision system that combines 4D and laser scanners, SLAM algorithms, event cameras, and advanced vision software to generate real time 4D images of road object; and VoxelFlow, a patented software for advanced four-dimensional image analysis of moving objects. The company was formerly known as TerraNet Holding AB (publ). Terranet AB was founded in 2004 and is headquartered in Lund, Sweden.
